tch the job by clicking \u0026ldquo;Match\u0026rdquo; button. Matching rate list between the selected job and acedemic staff will be listed out. Sort matching rate list by matching rate. Change the entries that will show the list in one page. Search academic staff by inputting the name. Redirect to the selected job by clicking the job name. Redirect to the scopuslink of selected academic staff by clicking the academic staff name.  Developed by Ye Jin Loh.\n","date":1632528e3,"expirydate":-62135596800,"kind":"page","lang":"en","lastmod":1632528e3,"objectID":"9b878d0913175fdf978f12fecf044371","permalink":"https://spozi.github.io/project/job-matcher-uum/","publishdate":"2021-09-25T00:00:00Z","relpermalink":"/project/job-matcher-uum/","section":"project","summary":"Matching a job based on one’s knowledge and experience is not a straightforward task. However, the degree of  difficulty for finding a job that suit each other is increasing dramatically over years. Therefore, a project is proposed to develop a system to match job with past achievements or proven experiences. This project is to provide an automated platform in matching jobs with past achievements or proven experiences to find right job candidates.","tags":["Word Embedding","Collaboration","Ye Jin Loh"],"title":"A Development of a System to Match Job with Past Scholarly Publications","type":"project"},{"authors":null,"categories":null,"content":"The content of this course is such as follows:\n","date":1632528e3,"expirydate":-62135596800,"kind":"page","lang":"en","lastmod":1632528e3,"objectID":"da0e023b93fa6d1039b734b9437b78bb","permalink":"https://spozi.github.io/teaching/machine-learning/","publishdate":"2021-09-25T00:00:00Z","relpermalink":"/teaching/machine-learning/","section":"teaching","summary":"This course is an undergraduate level course. Here, students will learn fundamental concept related to machine learning, as well as its applicability in solving real world problems.","tags":["machine learning","